Statistical analysis results of muscle-specific measures

Source: R/data.R
MUSCLES_STATS.Rd

A data.frame containing statistical analysis results of muscle-specific measures: terminal muscle mass, mean cross-sectional area (CSA), glycogen, capillary contacts, and citrate synthase.

MUSCLES_STATS

Format

An object of class tbl_df (inherits from tbl, data.frame) with 224 rows and 19 columns.

See also

MUSCLES, MUSCLES_EMM

Examples

unique(MUSCLES_STATS$response)
#> [1] "Capillary Contacts" "Citrate Synthase"   "Glycogen"          
#> [4] "Mean CSA"           "Terminal Weight"
